<title datatype="string">Oxidation of ammonia by Nitrosomonas europaea. Definite 18O-tracer evidence that hydroxylamine formation involves a monooxygenase.</title>
<year datatype="integer">1981</year>
<author datatype="string">Hollocher TC</author>
